Package serverSide.objects

This package contains the shared regions used by the Master Thief and Ordinary Thieves.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssaultParty
    Assault Party is constituted by Ordinary Thieves that are going to attack the museum.
    CollectionSite
    Collection Site where intelligence and paintings are stored.
    ConcentrationSite
    Concentration Site where ordinary thieves wait for orders.
    GeneralRepository
    General Repository where logging occurs.
    Museum
    The Museum has rooms inside it.
    RegisterRemoteObject
    Generic functionality to register in the local RMI registry service objects located in the same or other processing nodes of a parallel machine.
